stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initialization: Start Workflow
    
    Initialization: Initialize State<br/>Load Concepts<br/>Setup Metrics
    
    Initialization --> Generation: Begin Loop
    
    Generation: Generation Node<br/>- Find Similar Concepts<br/>- Generate Relationships
    
    Generation --> Validation: Pass Batches
    
    Validation: Validation Node<br/>- Validate Merges<br/>- Validate Relationships<br/>- Accumulate Valid<br/>- Track Weak Patterns
    
    Validation --> ConvergenceCheck: Check Status
    
    ConvergenceCheck: Convergence Decision<br/>Check new unique items
    
    ConvergenceCheck --> Generation: Continue (new items found)
    ConvergenceCheck --> Complete: Converged (0 new items)
    ConvergenceCheck --> Complete: Max iterations
    
    Complete: [*]
    
    note right of ConvergenceCheck
        Convergence when BOTH:
        - New merges = 0
        - New relationships = 0
    end note
